    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bengan Yes </h2>is an action-packed arena fighting game designed for livestreaming. Choose to either let your viewers brawl it out or simulate a clash between thousands of bots. Everyone has an equal chance of winning with both the arena and stats of players being randomized.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twitch interactive</h2>Set a custom keyword for your viewers to join a battle to the death, perfect for deciding giveaway winners!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simulate fights</h2>Add up to thousands of bots to clash for your own entertainment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomized conditions</h2>Enter a seed to generate a random arena along with randomized player stats.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Music</h2>Lifelike - Music by AlexiAction from Pixabay<br><br>Please Calm My Mind - Music by EvgenyBardyuzha from Pixabay<br>Password infinity - Music by Lesfm from Pixabay<br>Dragon Castle - Music by Makai Symphony<br>Bengan Bros menu song - &quot;Game Menu&quot; by Eric Matyas.<br>Bengan Bros puzzle song - &quot;Mind Bender&quot; by Eric Matyas<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Credits</h2>Addemannen1 - Main Developer<br><br>123meinkratf - 3D Artist lord<br>LucasNagy - Designer &amp; picture maker person<br>August - Marketing &amp; writing steam page person<br>ReeZey - Man of optimizing the game, making all UI and helping with other stuff too :)",
